Expected grouping
Application requirement
 Why we chose K = 2

Looking at your dataset:

(2,3), (3,4), (4,3)      → Group 1  
(10,10), (11,12), (9,11) → Group 2

 Clearly two natural groups exist

 Interpretation
Small values → Cluster 0
Large values → Cluster 1

 So K = 2 is logical and optimal
